      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it doesn't change the fact that it hurts. every morning i wake up and the first thing i feel is this crushing emptiness. it's like i'm just going through the motions, existing but not really living. sometimes i look at the empty spot on the floor where his bed used to be and i just think... what's the point of trying to \"get better\" when everything that mattered is just gone? it's so much work to keep moving through this.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
